    <h1>Structured Paths for Your Learning;</h1>
    <div class="timeline">
        <div class="container left-container">
            <img src="/img/dsa.png" alt="">
            <div class="text-box">
                <h2>Data Structures & Algorithms</h2>
                <small>    Time: 3-4 months</small>
                <p>Data Structures and Algorithms (DSA) is the backbone of programming, focusing on the study of structures that hold data and the algorithms that process it. It includes:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Arrays, Linked Lists, Stacks, Queues</li>
                        <li>Trees, Graphs, Hashing</li>
                        <li>Sorting and Searching Algorithms</li>
                        <li>Dynamic Programming</li>
                        <li>Greedy Algorithms</li>
                        <li>Backtracking</li>
                    </ul>
                    Understanding these concepts is critical for problem-solving in competitive programming.
                </p>
                <span class="left-container-arrow"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container right-container">
            <img src="/img/cpp.svg" alt="">
            <div class="text-box">
                <h2>C++</h2>
                <small>Time: 2 months</small>
                <p>C++ is a powerful language that is commonly used in competitive programming due to its efficiency and control over memory. Key topics to focus on include:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Syntax and Data Types</li>
                        <li>Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)</li>
                        <li>STL (Standard Template Library)</li>
                        <li>Memory Management</li>
                        <li>File Handling</li>
                    </ul>
                    Mastering C++ will significantly improve your performance in coding contests.
                </p>
                <span class="right-container-arrow"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container left-container">
            <img src="/img/java.jpg" alt="">
            <div class="text-box">
                <h2>java</h2>
                <small>Time: 2-3 months</small>
                <p>Java is a widely used object-oriented programming language known for its portability across platforms. It is important for handling large-scale applications and is also used in competitive programming. Key topics include:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Java Syntax and Data Types</li>
                        <li>Object-Oriented Principles</li>
                        <li>Collections Framework (Lists, Sets, Maps)</li>
                        <li>Concurrency and Multithreading</li>
                        <li>File I/O</li>
                    </ul>
                    Java's strong features make it suitable for solving complex problems.
                </p>
                <span class="left-container-arrow"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container right-container">
            <img src="/img/python.webp" alt="">
            <div class="text-box">
                <h2>Python</h2>
                <small>Time: 1-2 months</small>
                <p>Python is an easy-to-learn programming language with a rich set of libraries. Topics to cover include:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Python Basics (Syntax, Data Structures)</li>
                        <li>Libraries: NumPy, Pandas, Matplotlib</li>
                        <li>String Manipulation</li>
                        <li>File Handling and Regular Expressions</li>
                        <li>Algorithmic Problem Solving</li>
                    </ul>
                    Python is great for quick solutions and prototyping in competitive programming.
                </p>
                <span class="right-container-arrow"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container left-container">
            <img src="/img/html.jpg" alt="">
            <div class="text-box">
                <h2>HTML</h2>
                <small>Time: 2-3 weeks</small>
                <p>HTML is the foundational language of the web. You should learn:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Basic Tags: div, p, h1-h6, a, img, etc.</li>
                        <li>Forms and Inputs</li>
                        <li>HTML5 New Features</li>
                        <li>Semantic HTML</li>
                    </ul>
                    Understanding HTML is essential for building web pages and structuring content.
                </p>
                <span class="left-container-arrow"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container right-container">
            <img src="/img/css.webp" alt="">
            <div class="text-box">
                <h2>CSS</h2>
                <small>Time: 2-3 weeks</small>
                <p>CSS is used to style and layout web pages. Topics include:
                    <ul>
                        <li>CSS Selectors and Properties</li>
                        <li>Flexbox and Grid Layout</li>
                        <li>Responsive Design</li>
                        <li>Animations and Transitions</li>
                    </ul>
                    Mastering CSS is important for designing modern, responsive websites.
                </p>
                <span class="right-container-arrow"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container left-container">
            <img src="/img/js.webp" alt="">
            <div class="text-box">
                <h2>JavaScript</h2>
                <small>Time: 1-2 months</small>
                <p>JavaScript is essential for web development, making web pages interactive. Focus on:
                    <ul>
                        <li>JavaScript Syntax and Data Types</li>
                        <li>DOM Manipulation</li>
                        <li>Event Handling</li>
                        <li>Asynchronous JavaScript (Promises, async/await)</li>
                        <li>Frameworks: React.js, Node.js</li>
                    </ul>
                    Learning JavaScript opens up frontend and backend development opportunities.
                </p>
                <span class="left-container-arrow"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container right-container">
            <img src="/img/php.png" alt="">
            <div class="text-box">
                <h2>php</h2>
                <small>Time: 1 month</small>
                <p>PHP is a server-side scripting language widely used for web development. Key topics include:
                    <ul>
                        <li>PHP Syntax and Functions</li>
                        <li>MySQL Database Integration</li>
                        <li>Handling Forms and Sessions</li>
                        <li>Security Best Practices</li>
                        <li>Frameworks: Laravel</li>
                    </ul>
                    PHP is essential for backend development and dynamic website creation.
                </p>
                <span class="right-container-arrow"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
